chapter 1
   
        open panna night nerram montain area oru track pothu track full black money montain mella poitu iruku appo anga oru tea kadai iruku athudhaan last tea kadai so anga  poi driver 2 per tea kudichichaga appo anga oruthan vandhaan body full sathumannu apply pannitu vanthaan driver tea kudikirra nera ma pathu antha track ka theft pannitu poitan.
        driver rendu perum kudicha glass sa kellu pottu odi poi pedika ponnanum apo pudika mudiyama pistal gun na aduthu fire pannanum andha tea kadai owner nu shock la irudhar
        andha tea kadai bhai police ku call pannaru andhai pathu andha rendu per bhai ya fire panni tu owner ku call pannaga apponu pathu tower illa oru sinal dhaan iruthuchi athuvum sometime singal poi poi dhaan varum epo enna pannrathu theriyama andha area la std irukannu pathutu iruthanum............
        
